To install the st_pipeline on UPPMAX follow the instructions below:

1) Install virtual environment in your UPPMAX following this guideline (make sure you use python version 2.7.6):
   
https://www.uppmax.uu.se/how-to-install-your-own-python-modules-or-specific-python-version

2) Install bowtie2 (NOT NEEDED in Uppmax since you can load bowtie with module load bowtie but this will install the newest version) :

    cd pipeline/depedencies
    unzip bowtie2-2.2.3-source.zip
    cd bowtie2-2.2.3 
    make
    cp bowtie2* ~/bin

3) download the pipeline file on your computer from ST Google Docs

4) copy zip-file to your uppmax home folder

5) unzip the file on uppmax
	password: avgohe52 (version < 0.3.1)
	password: avghoe52 (version 0.3.1 and onwards)

6) run the commands:
  	cd pipeline
  	python setup.py build
  	python setup.py install
  	pyeven rehash    

7) test by running the command:
  	python setup.py test
